      relatedFaqSlugs: ["can-i-use-my-land-equity-as-the-down-payment-on-a-construction-loan", "land-and-construction-loan-arizona", "what-credit-score-do-i-need-for-a-construction-loan-in-arizona", "construction-loan-requirements-arizona"],
